{"tid":786934,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解尿兜會塞？","createTime":"2018-08-20T09:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T12:32:59.000Z","uid":15495,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb32096597e4c3b8b85ddc61524a10943f67a36","tid":786934,"uid":15495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"我公司啲尿兜成日塞，講緊係三個禮拜就塞一次，塞親都係塞晒幾個，好唔方便。 <br />\n<br />\n但係我諗下諗下，首先明明個尿兜入面應該唔會有固體嘅嘢係入面，就算有都會比個隔隔住咗，然後佢一塞就塞晒幾個尿兜，咁即係條大渠塞，但係我又真係見過我公司啲清潔呀姐通個尿兜，咁就算積垃圾都無理由咁快就積到塞㗎，何況應該都無咁大舊垃圾跌到落去條渠度，咁點解尿兜係會塞嘅？"},{"pid":"c41f7f50a13666e9ac13d03c702570bd85c7b2ba","tid":786934,"uid":17011,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"腎者之石"},{"pid":"a3d087c100cc214bdc4ed6ad26d6e5d8505f9159","tid":786934,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"毛"},{"pid":"7a8dd428ceb8827009008c476e41a87b3b8f2944","tid":786934,"uid":46007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"鳩毛"},{"pid":"0bd3db1fc1238678d21a039456850594304befc1","tid":786934,"uid":57524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"有人掉廁紙/紙巾落去"},{"pid":"fa27b1e2eb1dc55e610fd09cf1b8d47ddd3accf9","tid":786934,"uid":63843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"沼澤波子機"},{"pid":"6bf59f91592f2117d4ea0dc8ffed18f95c12a971","tid":786934,"uid":15495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a8dd428ceb8827009008c476e41a87b3b8f2944","tid":786934,"uid":46007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"鳩毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"即係條渠入面有條鳩毛墊，好似餅髮菜咁塞住條渠？"},{"pid":"b576460eb0ff57aec094438730b4e17343e3e451","tid":786934,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"有人疴屎落去"},{"pid":"c41f91075b916b75a3404e2ace12a44d0d945571","